timeline.bodyText:
would it be possible to avoid the symlink trick with the resources { } instruction? like below snippet (from #2520):
		resources {
			from("${sourceDir}/highlight") {
				into "./highlight/"
				include '**/*'
			}
			from("${sourceDir}/images") {
				into "./images/"
				include '**'
			}
			from( "${rootDir}/docs/svg" ) {
				into "./images/"
				include 'legend-*.svg'
			}
		}
